rows.label: qst001803_msg0001
rows.name:
Reid...
I'm so glad you're all right!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0002
rows.name: Sorry for worryin' you.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0003
rows.name:
Indeed. If you trained up and
got a little stronger, I wouldn't
have to worry so much.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0004
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]No! You've got to stop with that, Olua!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0005
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Didn't this just prove it?

rows.label: qst001803_msg0006
rows.name: I'm no Driver! Not yet!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I've got to get strong like these
guys before I can go off on
journeys and stuff!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]But the training trips are how
you become strong, Reid.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0009
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Aye, there's a limit!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0010
rows.name:
Let's travel AFTER I've learned how
to swordfight and what have you!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0011
rows.name: You've got it all backwards!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0012
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]It's like you're askin' me to make a
banquet when I can't even hold a knife.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]If you just put your mind to it, though...

rows.label: qst001803_msg0014
rows.name:
Everyone's got to start somewhere!
The most important thing is taking
the first step!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0015
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Ah...

rows.label: qst001803_msg0016
rows.name:
Let's talk about this later. We should
be thankful to these fine people.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0017
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I don't care, whatever!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0018
rows.name:
I'm goin' home!
You can do your trainin' mission alone!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Young man!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0020
rows.name:
Here's something by way of thanks.
I hope we meet again sometime
and we can talk properly.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0021
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Here's hoping they sort it out
eventually...
